{"tid":1567661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"915 交通事宜","createTime":"2019-09-14T06:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T11:47:56.000Z","uid":78465,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5b53a723cd708d92d4844dc3fb604171b25e6889","tid":1567661,"uid":78465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"依幾晚地區活動都有人呼籲915去維園，相信有部份和理非聽日都有興趣去港島行街<br />\n<br />\n去港島區相信都係搭鐵為主，相信啲狗聽日係港島大站一定大量部處，站內有咩動靜就會借機封站。封站阻嚇和理非出黎行街，亦令已經出左ge行街人士大為不便同好危險<br />\n<br />\n或借聽日日間要儘量避免係地鐵站有任何行動? 連係站內等人都唔好以免被狗借機生事?今個星期日日歌唱大會有效集結示威意志，所以啲狗先咁驚黎多次超大型遊行。政府咁驚，更加應該做多次818效果<br />\n<br />\n行動組可考慮較後時間先開始，等行街人士安心?<br />\n利申:全力支持星期六日搞9黨鐵，血債血償<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930b0565926a1950812467f6b010387787b5068a","tid":1567661,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:50:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3aaa4abdd6c05dec9989fbff3abe60655d4f680","tid":1567661,"uid":313318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:00:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f90eabb9d1843902f3b46bb3635eaf1b39d985b","tid":1567661,"uid":78465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:12:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4ce20ded100a311c918354c8b4c262c63a9eec47","tid":1567661,"uid":276535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:19:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69f53b356eafd817b583773b955a074b42060c08","tid":1567661,"uid":78465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:02:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"